Principal hosts. Undefinable.
A . glasgowi
does not exhibit the host specificity and infests a wide range of hosts, including diverse taxa of rodents, bats, small carnivores and insectivores (
Strandtmann, 1949
;
Evans & Till, 1966
;
Zemskaya, 1973
;
Goncharova et al ., 1991
).

Distribution. Cosmopolitan (
Evans & Till, 1966
). In Asiatic Russia , it is widely distributed (
Nikulina, 2004
).
